data.description: Remarkable Hemet property! A MUST SEE! Nestled on 4.47 acres, you will find all the luxuries and comforts you have been searching for, with space for all your toys! Kitchen is complete with a neighboring dining room, and comes equipped with upgrades, stunning oversized kitchen island, walk-in pantry, Recessed lighting in all the bedrooms with window views of your property oasis. Ceiling fans. All bathrooms are upgraded. Front and back entry doors have security gates, landscaping includes cement walk-ways and slab for gazebo, upgraded front and back decks, beautiful Mountain View’s. Outdoor beautiful guest bathroom addition, Property is fully fenced on all sides! Minutes away from the Temecula Wineries!
